boogu-image-swift
Copyright 2026 Xocialize

Swift/MLX port of Boogu-Image-0.1 (Apache-2.0): a Qwen3-VL-8B-conditioned
OmniGen2-lineage DiT (8 double-stream + 32 single-stream blocks) + FLUX.1
AutoencoderKL (16-channel) + FlowMatchEuler static-v1 time-shift scheduler.
Surfaces textToImage (Base / Turbo) and imageEdit (Edit) as one MLXEngine
ModelPackage.

Reference implementation: the parity-locked Python-MLX port
xocialize/boogu-image-mlx (Apache-2.0). The Qwen3-VL conditioner is reused from
the xocialize/qwen3vl-mlx-swift backbone (which itself adapts mlx-swift-lm's
MLXVLM Qwen3VL, Apache-2.0). The VAE follows diffusers' AutoencoderKL.

Boogu-Image-0.1 model weights: Apache-2.0, published at
mlx-community/Boogu-Image-0.1-{Base,Turbo,Edit}-* and the conditioner at
mlx-community/Qwen3-VL-8B-Instruct. This repository contains no model weights.
